        <item>
          <title>Apple Music Classical Now Available on Web Browsers - A Game-Changer for Mac Users?</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Apple Music Classical is now available to stream via web browsers, marking the first platform to receive a designated space since iPad and CarPlay in 2023 and 2024. However, there's still no news on when Mac devices will get a native app for the service.]]></description>
